parameters: \n<Bandit a>"Is that the last of the food we carried over?"

\n<Bandit b>"Yeah. We had quite the haul today. We're getting pretty
good at hunting, aren't we?"

\n<Bandit a>"Not sure if I should be happy about it... This is just like
living a hunter's life."

\n<Bandit c>"Can't help it. Our leader isn't going to open the road to
the town side for just any reason.... Now, let's hurry up
and carry it inside."

\n<Lyric>"Oh, there are people over there. They don't look like
townsfolk, maybe they're bandits?"

\n<Ameria>"Probably. But they were saying something strange, weren't
they?"

\n<Roselitte>"Yes. Something about not opening the road to the town side.
Could they be blocking the way to Annabern?"

\n<Ameria>"...What do we do, Roselitte-san? Should we take a detour
and look for another path?"

\n<Roselitte>"Hmm... Considering the size of this mountain pass and the
time we'd lose... Perhaps we should 'have a talk' with
them."

\n<Lyric>"Nope. Looking for another path sounds tough too, so I
agree."
\n<Roselitte>"Alright. Then both of you, stay sharp."
